ZH: 圣母是天主教中对圣母玛利亚的尊称。
EN: The Virgin Mary is revered as the Blessed Mother in Catholicism.

ZH: 在我们村庄的教堂前，有一座圣母像。
EN: There is a statue of the Virgin Mary in front of our village church.

ZH: 多年来，许多人来朝圣敬奉圣母。
EN: Over the years, many people have come on pilgrimage to worship the Virgin Mary.

ZH: 我们每年都会举办一个盛大的庆祝会，以纪念圣母。
EN: We organize a grand celebration every year to commemorate the Virgin Mary.

ZH: 圣母被认为是众生的庇佑者。
EN: The Virgin Mary is considered the protector of all beings.

ZH: 在圣母的庇护下，我们感到平安和宁静。
EN: Under the protection of the Virgin Mary, we feel safe and peaceful.

ZH: 圣母在许多宗教文学和艺术作品中被描绘得十分美丽。
EN: The Virgin Mary is often depicted as exceptionally beautiful in religious literature and artistic works.

ZH: 圣母的形象在信徒心中代表着慈悲和宽容。
EN: The image of the Virgin Mary represents compassion and forgiveness in the hearts of believers.

ZH: 圣母马利亚被奉为天主教的宠儿。
EN: The Virgin Mary is regarded as the beloved child of Catholicism.

ZH: 亲近圣母马利亚的信仰给人们带来了无尽的祝福。
EN: Devotion to the Virgin Mary brings endless blessings to people.

ZH: 圣母被誉为母亲的榜样，给予我们力量和鼓励。
EN: The Virgin Mary is hailed as a role model of motherhood, giving us strength and encouragement.

ZH: 在诸多灾难和困境中，信徒们常向圣母祈祷，寻求庇佑。
EN: In times of calamity and hardship, believers often pray to the Virgin Mary, seeking her protection.

ZH: 圣母岛是爱尔兰的一个朝圣地，吸引着众多信徒和游客。
EN: The Island of the Virgin Mary is a pilgrimage site in Ireland, attracting many believers and tourists.

ZH: 这座教堂以圣母的名字命名，是一个宗教遗址。
EN: The church, named after the Virgin Mary, is a religious site.

ZH: 我们将在明天的弥撒中，向圣母献上我们的祷告。
EN: Tomorrow during Mass, we will offer our prayers to the Virgin Mary.

ZH: 圣母教堂的建立是一个重要的宗教事件。
EN: The establishment of the Church of the Virgin Mary is a significant religious event.

ZH: 信徒们每年都会举办一个盛大的烛光游行，以纪念圣母。
EN: Every year, believers organize a grand candlelight procession to commemorate the Virgin Mary.

ZH: 圣母的故事在圣经中被详细描述。
EN: The story of the Virgin Mary is detailed in the Bible.

ZH: 圣母的祈祷被认为是非常灵验的。
EN: The prayers to the Virgin Mary are considered highly effective.

ZH: 圣母的荣誉和尊敬与她的令人敬畏的品质相称。
EN: The honor and respect bestowed upon the Virgin Mary befit her awe-inspiring qualities.
